<H3> <TI>   Energy Efficiency Engineers Graduate </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Energy Efficiency Engineers Graduate </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL1504003494 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 2300 
GMT 14 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1504003494 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Our country's first graduate course on energy 
efficiency has concluded at the Cienfuegos Higher Technical 
Institute following almost three years of academic and practical 
training. 
  Joel Domenech, president of the National Energy Commission, 
participated in the graduation ceremony for 17 electrical, 
chemical, thermal-energy, and mechanical engineers from various 
centers of economic importance in Cienfuegos Province. 

</TEXT>

