<H3> <TI>   President Comments on Freeing of Kidnapped American, Lack of </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    President Comments on Freeing of Kidnapped American, Lack of </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
U.S.   Aid 

<F P=102> PA1804223594 Guatemala City Teleonce Television in Spanish 
0400 GMT 18 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1804223594 </F>
<F P=104>  Guatemala City Teleonce Television </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>
