  [Text] Buenos Aires, 18 Apr (NA) -- President Carlos Menem 
tonight denied suffering a heart problem during the past few 
hours, which, according to persistent rumors, obliged him to 
undergo an urgent operation. 
  "I am very well; that rumor must have been put about by 
someone who wants me to die," Menem said a few minutes ago from 
the Olivos Residence over the state television channel. 

