<H3> <TI>   Raul Castro Attends Western Army Military Council </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Raul Castro Attends Western Army Military Council </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL2004011294 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 2300 
GMT 19 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2004011294 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Army General Raul Castro Ruz, second secretary of 
the Cuban Communist Party Central Committee, and defense 
minister of the Cuban Revolutionary Armed Forces, is attending 
work sessions of the special military council of the Eastern 
Army, which is analyzing the experience of this unit in using 
alternative energy sources. 
  This council is also discussing the efforts being made to 
save fuel, at the same time outlining directives to intensify 
the energy program in military units. 

</TEXT>

